Something big is coming soon. Owen records will be dropping the most anticipated single of the year “Snapchat” soon. This is more than something light, it’s hotter than fire. Snapchat, an Afro Folk melodic tune infused with Nigerian traditional feels will make anyone stand up and dance anytime. Chucky Kelvin sticking with his melodic singing style, comes out big with this banger. Snapchat is currently rocking the streets nationwide and Kelvin is set to go on a nationwide radio tour soon. 